### 1) 登录
POST http://127.0.0.1:48080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": 1,
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456",
  "terminal": "ADMIN"
}

### 2) 刷新 token
POST http://127.0.0.1:48080/auth/token/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 3) 使用 accessToken 调用动态菜单
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/system/menu/tree
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4) 按钮权限
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/system/permission/buttons
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 5) 在线会话列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/auth/sso/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 6) 按 sessionId 强制下线
POST http://127.0.0.1:48080/auth/sso/kickout/session?sessionId={{sessionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 7) 权限点校验
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/auth/permission/check?permission=system:user:query
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 8) 接口级权限拦截示例：用户列表（需 system:user:query）
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/system/user/list
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 9) 接口级权限拦截示例：创建用户（需 system:user:create）
POST http://127.0.0.1:48080/system/user/create
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "new_user",
  "nickname": "新用户"
}

### 10) 接口级权限拦截示例：更新用户（需 system:user:update）
PUT http://127.0.0.1:48080/system/user/update
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 2,
  "username": "ops",
  "nickname": "运维管理员-更新"
}

### 11) 网关审计统计（管理员）
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/gateway/audit/stats?retentionDays=30
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 12) 手动触发网关审计归档（管理员）
POST http://127.0.0.1:48080/gateway/audit/archive/run?retentionDays=30&batchSize=500
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 13) 审计日志分页查询（主表）
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/gateway/audit/logs?archived=false&pageNo=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 14) 审计日志分页查询（归档表 + 时间区间）
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/gateway/audit/logs?archived=true&startTime=2026-01-01%2000:00:00&endTime=2026-12-31%2023:59:59&pageNo=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 15) 审计日志导出 CSV（管理员）
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/gateway/audit/logs/export?archived=false&maxRows=5000
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 16) 创建异步导出任务（管理员）
POST http://127.0.0.1:48080/gateway/audit/export/tasks?archived=false&maxRows=5000
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 17) 查询异步导出任务状态（管理员）
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/gateway/audit/export/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 18) 下载异步导出结果（管理员）
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/gateway/audit/export/tasks/{{taskId}}/download
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 19) 手动清理导出任务（管理员）
POST http://127.0.0.1:48080/gateway/audit/export/tasks/cleanup/run?retentionDays=7&batchSize=500
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 20) 分页查询异步导出任务（管理员）
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/gateway/audit/export/tasks/list?status=SUCCESS&archived=false&pageNo=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 21) 分页查询异步导出任务（关键字 + 排序）
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/gateway/audit/export/tasks/list?keyword=gateway-audit-export&sortBy=finishedAt&sortOrder=desc&pageNo=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 22) 分页查询异步导出任务（按租户+用户筛选）
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/gateway/audit/export/tasks/list?tenantId=1&userId=1&pageNo=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 23) 分页查询异步导出任务（按导出条件 success 筛选）
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/gateway/audit/export/tasks/list?success=1&pageNo=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

