  "password": "123456",
  "terminal": "MP"
}

### 29) 小程序端接口（需 MEMBER + MP）
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/mp/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{mpAccessToken}}

### 30) 第三方 OpenAPI（签名鉴权）
# sign 计算：HMAC_SHA256(method + "\n" + path + "\n" + query + "\n" + timestamp + "\n" + nonce, appSecret)
# 示例：method=GET path=/openapi/v1/ping query=
# 响应头可观测：X-RateLimit-Limit / X-RateLimit-Remaining / X-RateLimit-Reset
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/openapi/v1/ping
X-App-Key: demo_app_key
X-Timestamp: {{epochSeconds}}
X-Nonce: {{nonce}}
X-Sign: {{openapiSign}}

### 31) 第三方 OpenAPI（会员摘要）
# query 参与签名：memberId=3
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/openapi/v1/member/summary?memberId=3
X-App-Key: demo_app_key
X-Timestamp: {{epochSeconds}}
X-Nonce: {{nonce}}
X-Sign: {{openapiSignWithQuery}}

### 32) Infra 模块：基础设施状态
GET http://127.0.0.1:48080/infra/config/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

